base:     basic system files that belong in /bin /usr/bin and /usr/lib     [IMP]
comms:    serial file-transfer protocols and communication packages        [REC]
efs2:     utilities for creating and repairing the improved ext. file sys. [REC]
etc:      system administration utilities that belong in /etc              [IMP]
getty:    controls the process of logging in to your system                [IMP]
joe:      an easy to text-editor, similar to Wordstar(tm)                  [REC]
national: change the font and keyboard on the virtual consoles             [OPT]
select14: kernel patch and util for "cut and paste" on virtual consoles    [REC]
vgalib:   library for [S]VGA graphics under Linux without X11              [REC]
